---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Access Control | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Cloud-managed access control from Verkada. Blue Cap IT installs door controllers, card readers, and mobile credentials. Verkada Gold Partner. Call (410) 858-4031.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Access Control</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Access <span class="grad">Control</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">Cloud-managed door controllers, smart readers, and mobile credentials. Control who gets in — from anywhere, in real time.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get an Access Control Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/241017_Access_Control_Family_hard_shadow.png" alt="Verkada Access Control" class="feature-img"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual">
            <div class="feature-visual-bg"></div>
            <img src="/AC12-AllContollers_FrontStaggered.png" alt="Verkada Door Controllers" style="max-width:380px;width:100%;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.6));border-radius:8px;"/>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Cloud-First Door Management</h3>
            <p>Verkada's access control is managed entirely in the cloud through Verkada Command. Add users, assign access levels, and unlock doors from your phone — no on-site server needed.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Remote unlock from any device, anywhere</li>
              <li>Instant credential provisioning &amp; revocation</li>
              <li>Scheduled access rules &amp; time-based permissions</li>
              <li>Full audit trail of every door event</li>
              <li>Unified with cameras for visual verification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual">
            <div class="feature-visual-bg"></div>
            <img src="/241017_Access_Control_Family_hard_shadow.png" alt="Verkada Card Readers and Credentials" style="max-width:420px;width:100%;filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));border-radius:8px;"/>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Modern Credential Options</h3>
            <p>Offer employees and visitors the credential experience that works for them — from traditional keycards to smartphone-based mobile access, Apple Watch, and PIN codes.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>RFID card &amp; fob credentials</li>
              <li>Mobile credentials via Verkada Pass app</li>
              <li>Apple Watch &amp; wearable support</li>
              <li>PIN code entry &amp; QR code visitor access</li>
              <li>Biometric reader support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🔗</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Seamless Camera Integration</h3>
            <p>Every access event is linked to a camera clip — instantly see who badged through any door, on any day, in seconds. True unified physical security.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Auto-linked video clip for every door event</li>
              <li>One-click jump from access log to camera footage</li>
              <li>Tailgating &amp; forced door alerts</li>
              <li>Door-held-open notifications</li>
              <li>Integrated with alarms and sensors</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Hardware</div>
      <h2>Access Control <span class="grad">Hardware</span></h2>
      <div class="specs-grid">
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/access-control/family.png" alt="Verkada Access Control product family" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Door Controllers</h4><ul><li>AC12 single-door controller</li><li>AC42 multi-door controller</li><li>PoE powered — no separate PSU</li><li>Fail-secure &amp; fail-safe modes</li><li>Tamper detection built-in</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/access-control/prox-card-reader.jpg" alt="Verkada AD32 prox card reader" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Card Readers</h4><ul><li>OSDP &amp; Wiegand support</li><li>LED &amp; audible feedback</li><li>Indoor &amp; outdoor variants</li><li>Touch keypad available</li><li>Sleek modern design</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>🔒 Door Hardware</h4><ul><li>Electric strikes &amp; maglocks</li><li>Panic bar integration</li><li>Glass door compatibility</li><li>Elevator control support</li><li>Gate controller options</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/access-control/apple-wallet.png" alt="Apple Wallet mobile credential for Verkada access control" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Biometric Readers</h4><ul><li>Fingerprint readers</li><li>Facial recognition entry</li><li>HIPAA-compliant options</li><li>Anti-spoofing technology</li><li>Cloud-enrolled biometrics</li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Secure Your Doors</div>
    <h2>Start with a Free <span class="grad">Access Control Assessment</span></h2>
    <p>Blue Cap IT will evaluate your facility, recommend the right Verkada access control solution, and handle installation end-to-end.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Request Free Assessment</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
